reviewText: When it comes to Playboy video's, I really don't get excited.  But I was at a party, and one of the guys had this video.  It is probably the best Playboy Video ever made. It is tastefully done, and the women are beutiful.  This is a must have for any man's video collection.
the best playboy film too date
excellent viewing from days gone by.

I bought this for Vanessa Conner as I thought she was beautiful from the magazine.
Since she was on the cover I thought she would be featured, but she was not she was in it for a few minutes in a group and not nude. I'm amazed that Playboy has all these beautiful women to make videos with and do such a bad job. This is not the first time Playboy has failed in making a video.

There's both a nice quantity & quality of girls on here for just about an hour of footage.  Plenty of natural looking girls is a def. plus. One of my favorite, heck maybe my favorite Playboy video not featuring Playmates (with the exception of Julie Cialini).

Playboy's Girls of Radio Rock Talk & Shock is fifty-eight minutes and was rereleased on DVD on June 15, 1999. The video features the following ladies:

Amy Lynn Baxter- Howard Stern Girl WXRK 92.3 FM New York, NY (Penthouse Pet of the Month for June 1990
Kimberly Egler-Promo Girl KSJO 92.3 FM San Jose, CA
Kat McNenna-Promo Girl XTRA 91X FM San Diego, CA
Catherine Shaw-Promo Girl XTRA 91X FM San Diego, CA
Julie Lynn Cialini-WCMF, 96.5 FM Rochester, New York (Playboy Playmate of the Month for February 1994 & Playboy Playmate of the Year for 1995)
Seka-Talk Show Hostess WLUP 97.9 Chicago,
Tempest-Howard Stern Girl WXRK 92.3 FM New York, NY
Tracy Ray-Talk Show Host WFTL 1400 AM Ft. Lauderdale, FL
Vanessa Conner-On Air Talent WHHH 96.3 FM Indianapolis, IN
Malissa Champine-News Producer Detroit, Mich
Diane Ray-On Air Talent WSHE 103.5 Miami, FL
Tricia Thomas-On Air Talent WHTZ 100.3 FM New York, NY
Guadalupe Davina-On Air Talent KXEB 91.0 Dallas, TX
Lizz Cufari-Marketing Director WAQY 102.1 FM Springfield, IL
Janet Layne-On Air Talent Springfield, MO
Karen Nobis-Account Executive KLAW 101.5 FM Lawton, OK
Jennifer Masterman-Contest Winner WUFX FM 103.3 Buffalo, NY
Dana Datillo-Contest Winner WEBN 102.7 FM Cincinnati, OH
Tonja Schild-Promo Girl KLOL 101 FM Houston, TX
Jessica Lee-Promo Girl WXTB 98 FM Clearwater, FL (Playboy Playmate of the Month for August 1996)
Joy Pons-Traffic Girl WQSR 105.7 FM Baltimore, MD
Shelly Jones-On Air Talent Ron & Ron Radio Network
Girls of Cheetah-96 Rock, WKLS 96.1 FM Atlanta, GA
Felecia-KLOS 95.1 FM Los Angeles, CA

Most of the ladies are pleasing to the eyes. The big finish is with the Cheetah Girls of 96 Rock and the gentlemen club performing their acts. Her are the ladies in the following order of the video.

Kimberly Egler, Kat McNenna, Catherine Shaw, & Julie Lynn Cialini-All four start out wearing sexy pajamas and lingerie. First the pajamas go and all four become topless. Only Kimberly and Julie become fully nude and the other are only semi-nude.
Amy Lynn Baxter & Tempest-Tempest is nude in the shower and Amy quickly becomes nude and is shaving herself. Both ladies eventually wind up in the bathtub giving each other a bath.
Tracy Ray-Tracy starts out wearing a black workout outfit and begins to strip it off. She does a nude workout in the firs scene. In the second scene Tracy is wearing a white one piece bathing suit. She slowly takes it off and becomes nude in the steam room.
Vanessa Conner, Malissa Champine, Diane Ray, Tricia Thomas & Guadalupe Davina-After the introduction are done, all five ladies become nude or semi-nude and do not share equal air time.
Lizz Cufari-The segment starts off with Lizz wearing white working clothes. In the next scene she is completely nude.
Janet Layne-Slowly becomes topless and quickly becomes totally nude.
Karen Nobis-Karen starts out wearing a red bra and skirt and becomes topless and eventually nude. She has a very short segment.
Jennifer Masterman, Dana Datillo, Tonja Schild, & Jessica Lee-During the introductions of all four ladies, each one is wearing sexy lingerie and become topless. After the phone call all four ladies are nude.
Joy Pons-Joy is fully nude 50% of the time.
Shelly Jones-Very little nudity
Seka-The couple in the video are nude, but Seka is not.
The Girls of Cheetah
Jessica-Fully nude
Madison-Nude
Star-Topless and then fully nude
Cody-Partial nudity
Kelly-Topless and then fully nude
Sebastian-Full nudity
Kendall-Topless and then nude
Shandra-Nude
Kerri-Nude
Jenny-Full nudity

Watch it only for the profession ladies and not the radio personalities. Playboy's Girls of Radio Rock Talk & Shock gets an A+.

I believe this is one of the hottest titles Playboy has ever produced. It actually has good music, which helps inspire the models and I love the mix of amateur "first time nude" Radio personalities who are really hot and professional nude models. Very unique for a Playboy produced title. The first segment featuring "Stomp-It's always Live" is the best I believe, and blisteringly hot with all 4 ladies dancing very erotic & sexy. These babes really know how to  move their bodies very seductively and smoking hot to the slow beat of the track, as well as vamp it up when looking at the camera. So hot! The rest of the DVD is really good too with the end coming with a nudel model competition sponsored by a local radio station. Well worth your time!

This dvd has it all...
Great music, great camera work, great videos & beautiful women...

I have watched it over and over again... it never gets old...

I can attest it is one of the best playboy dvd's out there...
Thanks...
